  <brief_title>Quantification and Derivation of Metabolic Needs in Children During Burn Rehabilitation</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Shriners Hospitals for Children</agency>
      <agency_class>Other</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Shriners Hospitals for Children</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators are collecting information on the calorie needs of patients in the first
      year postburn. The investigators hypothesize that increased energy needs continue for up to a
      year following wound closure from burn injury.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
